WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.533 --> 00:00:02.800
Junior brother, I have made the bed for you.

2
00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:03.933
You're staying here tonight?

3
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:06.133
Thank you for helping me look good in front of the elders today

4
00:00:06.133 --> 00:00:08.366
It's okay, just thank you.

5
00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:10.866
What do you want to say?

6
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.500
Are you really keeping out the cold?

7
00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:14.266
But the cold is dead

8
00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.366
Just two people who look the same

9
00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:18.300
Just to thank you for saving my life

10
00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:21.566
But are you really here to learn medicine?

11
00:00:21.566 --> 00:00:23.400
Of course. Isn't there anything else?

12
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:24.800
What you want to elaborate on

13
00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:26.833
Actually I think

14
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:30.666
Master Jiang Yifeng

15
00:00:31.133 --> 00:00:32.966
Fortunately, you are a gentleman

16
00:00:32.966 --> 00:00:34.966
If you are half confused about your senior sister

17
00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:36.633
I'll break your legs

18
00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:39.133
My sister looks much younger than me

19
00:00:39.133 --> 00:00:40.600
It should be called Junior Sister

20
00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:41.833
I started before you

21
00:00:41.866 --> 00:00:43.266
You should call me Senior Sister

22
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:46.400
The master looks very small too.

23
00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:48.266
I just celebrated my 100th birthday.

24
00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:49.300
Not young anymore

25
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.266
100.

26
00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:53.166
My secret recipe for Tianmen is the technique that can last forever

27
00:00:53.166 --> 00:00:55.300
You want to learn the art of removing demons and reducing demons

28
00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:56.000
That's not true.

29
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.433
The master only teaches the art of grass bones

30
00:00:57.666 --> 00:00:59.533
If you want to learn to fight and kill

31
00:00:59.533 --> 00:01:00.566
No chance

32
00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:02.100
So to speak

33
00:01:02.100 --> 00:01:03.566
I didn't worship Zuo Shimen

34
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:04.866
Why do you say that?

35
00:01:04.933 --> 00:01:06.366
Cultivation of immortals

36
00:01:06.366 --> 00:01:08.200
I don't necessarily have to subdue demons

37
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.700
Guangji people are also righteous

38
00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:11.433
You're right to think so

39
00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:13.066
But you're going to die soon.

40
00:01:13.133 --> 00:01:14.566
I won't live more than a month

41
00:01:14.766 --> 00:01:15.366
What!

42
00:01:15.366 --> 00:01:17.900
I didn't know that day what the glow on his chest was

43
00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:21.033
But you can see that it is absorbing his life

44
00:01:21.333 --> 00:01:22.800
Master, then you save junior brother

45
00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:23.933
I don't want my brother to die

46
00:01:23.933 --> 00:01:25.700
He came to worship me

47
00:01:25.700 --> 00:01:27.500
The only one who can save him is me

48
00:01:27.733 --> 00:01:28.966
You have a way to save him

